duties_responsibilities.duty: Handle cash transactions, fuel transactions, cleaning, and stocking items.
Perform food prep tasks and ensure foodservice safety for specific roles.
Interact with customers in a friendly and professional manner.
Maintain a clean and customer-ready store environment.
Promote and handle loyalty program rewards for customers.
Follow proper health code guidelines and ensure food preparation meets standards.
Perform repeated bending, standing, reaching, and occasionally lift up to 50 pounds.
